</p>
</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA12d064n1-ptr" id="PJA12d064n1">1</a>
<p>These were the joint commissions to accept the Austro-Russian mediation and to negotiate an Anglo-American peace and the instructions for the peace negotiations, all dated <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-11-02-0276" class="document">15 June</a> (vol. 11:368377).</p>
